The paper proposes a space-time block code (STBC) for multiple-input multiple-output (MIMO) systems, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and system and control theory (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the decoding complexity of the proposed code, which is related to networked and internet systems (cs.NI). Additionally, the paper focuses on MIMO systems with 4 transmit and 2 receive antennas, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM) and communication (cs.COM) systems.
